video.title: What Went Down
video.synopsis: Catch some of the world's most epic stunts and cringe-worthy sports bloopers, from amazing skydiving feats to painful parkour runs.

episodes.synopsis: Cameras capture astounding amateur lumberjacks, parkour stunts on the playground, wintertime snow pranks and motorcycles at a zoo.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Pete introduces a motorcycle doing an impossible backflip over a plane, bridge jumps gone wrong, football feats from Dude Perfect and a hot tub car.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: This set of stunt clips includes mind-boggling basketball shots, trampoline tragedies, a driverless car doing spinouts and a man stuck to a bike.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Stunts included in this episode involve winning BMX ramp successes, miserable parkour wall fails and a stilt-wearing skateboarder.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Head-shaking clips include zip line tricks, rope swing flops, high divers jumping from 75 feet and a birthday party for kittens.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Get ready to witness epic waterslide flips, embarrassing karate kicks, a high-five trick and an Amish guy jumping from an airplane.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Pete shows crazy clips including base jump wins, lame gymnastics, water park tricks from Dude Perfect and a trumpet-playing bear.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: This episode's stunts include high-elevation aerobatics, an angry whale and a small boat, low-level bike fails and wakeboarding in a public fountain.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Head-shaking clips include cool golf trick shots, a 50-foot cliff drop by a guy on a sled and a car towed by a dude walking on his hands.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: In addition to amazing long boarding and roller-skating videos, Pete shows an attempted 120-yard jump by a Mini car and a 1,300-pound pumpkin drop.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: In this episode, cameras focus on base jumpers extraordinaire, parkour losers, a break dancer with fireworks on his feet and a mountain unicycler.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: This episode includes cool ski jumps and a hot game of bowling with human balls and pins, plus a girl waking up her friend with a dead body.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Catch breathtaking rope swings from a huge cliff, pathetic golfers, a monster truck tug-of-war and juggling tricks with a cat's help.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Pete introduces talented slack line walkers, snow ski losers, a paraglider tangled in a power line and some monks having a snowball fight.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: This set of feats includes terrifying skydiving tricks, gymnastic fails, a bodybuilding trumpet player and a guy in a Gandalf costume sledding.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: In this episode, BMX tricks rule, parkour attempts flop, a truck and a tractor playing tug-of-war wind up in flames and Santa enjoys Slip 'N Slide.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: This set of stunts includes cool ski jumps, major ATV dumps, a kid zip lining from a skyscraper and Santa getting his beard caught in a rappel rope.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Watch high-flying basketball dunks, in-line skating crashes and a sky diver landing in a swamp. See a roommate's reaction to a big surprise.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Pete talks through great base jumpers, awful skateboarders, a bee-wearing bicyclist and the Dude Perfect guys using dynamite on 150 pounds of flour.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: This set of close calls includes skiers meeting avalanches, BMXers missing ramps and a dog getting sprayed by a hose-wielding bear.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: In this episode, the guys from Dude Perfect demonstrate trick shots, motorcyclists dump their bikes, and kayaks take to city streets instead of water.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Pete talks through awesome hoverboard tricks, not-so-tricky gymnastic attempts, guys riding high-speed trikes down a hill and a cat on a toilet.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: This set of fails includes high-altitude basketball dunks, low-elevation rollerblade thumps, a skydiver's swamp dive and a room filled with balloons.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Timing is the theme of this episode, which features synchronized parkour, a 200-foot bridge rope jump and Oreo cookie trick shots.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Guest Devin Graham shows insane water catapulting, while Pete focuses on sad trampoline tricks, a dirt bike's triple flip and a hot-air balloon crash.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Today's feats include mind-bending BMX tricks, humiliating unicycle fails, a Mini Cooper doing a backflip and a guy with fireworks blowing up a pool.
episodes.title: Episode 26
